r\n以前項方法得財產上不法之利益或使第三人得之者，亦同。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c114%2c20220809%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDM,111,簡,114,20220809,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"114","JDATE":"20220809","JTITLE":"詐欺"}